title: Beautiful waterfall
review: On the way to nainital is woodland waterfall. The waterfall is very beautiful. The view if water falling is amazing.

title: Very nice artificial waterfall..
review: This is a beautiful waterfall and a great place for a family picnic... The view is just awesome and the cool breeze is amazing

title: Nice, could have been better
review: There is entry fee to this place, they charge around 60 INR per person. Nothing too unique about the place but could be fun place for kids to enjoy waterfall.
